{"tid":1432477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★下年度公屋綠置居減至6100伙　等上樓雪上加霜","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19704e7ac5f7c45ba6f7c9d361e1fc0eda6b003a","tid":1432477,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"房屋委員會公布2019/20至2023/24年度的公營房屋建設計劃，平均每年出租公屋及綠置居供應量約1.4萬個單位，資助出售房屋平均每年4700間，整體平均供應量與前一個5年期的公營房屋建設計劃相若。<br />\n<br />\n當中2020/21年度的出租公屋及綠置居<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>由之前的1.1萬間，降至6100間</strong></span>，約一半單位延遲至2021/22年度落成。公屋聯會擔心，該年度有大量單位延遲落成，對於公屋輪候時間雪上加霜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/bkn-20190808153805916-0808_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190808%2Fbkn-20190808153805916-0808_00822_001.html&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7w7Fv2waV%2FkF2w15sEbuDLw%3D&h=3b1c6d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/bkn-20190808153805916-0808_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cdf3a0008cfc46f140d37e792c9ddf08c58e602e","tid":1432477,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659287027b95906782956f93ef26f2f25494ad70","tid":1432477,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"站出黎反對官商勾結地產霸權暴政啦"},{"pid":"9e4ff708414068661c8c875a8675e636b4fec61a","tid":1432477,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"公屋我話鳩知佢少定無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢起幾多都係比哂蝗<br />\n你起居屋好鳩過啦 起碼都叫Fair<br />\n有儲錢有得玩"}]}